{"tid":2087110,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"胡錫進：國安法打擊的是與境外勢力勾結起來破壞香港穩定的極端勢力，四種犯罪與言論、集會、結社等自由根本不沾邊","createTime":"2020-06-30T14:50:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T17:13:03.000Z","uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c3382caf6623bd30e5faea8ad2264988b6055bc8","tid":2087110,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T14:50:53.000Z","msg":"胡錫進：&ldquo;它打擊的是與境外勢力勾結起來破壞香港穩定的極少數極端勢力，它列出的四種犯罪與言論、集會、結社等自由根本不沾邊。它將構建起防止香港成為亞洲最動盪 城市的一道屏障。在這道屏障之內，構成香港活力的民主、自由、多元、開放等各種元素不僅不會受到壓制，反而會得到更加充分的釋放。香港的未來應當是作為與內地不同 的獨特城市大放異彩，繼續發揮國際金融中心的作用。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://finance.sina.cn/2020-06-30/detail-iirczymk9792243.d.html?from=wap\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffinance.sina.cn%2F2020-06-30%2Fdetail-iirczymk9792243.d.html%3Ffrom%3Dwap&d=6wD9ZzBID4i2v0E%2BCeDzwPUbXA8pdDK36CymbYVYMuw%3D&h=2e2bd9ab\" target=\"_blank\">https://finance.sina.cn/2020-06-30/detail-iirczymk9792243.d.html?from=wap</a>"},{"pid":"3d43e14e93712250b6b67f3cabbf51c124186f00","tid":2087110,"uid":302471,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T14:51:30.000Z","msg":"收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c21a10a56ff789ac11ea6eafb10d7dff53711e6f","tid":2087110,"uid":38528,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T14:52:11.000Z","msg":"屌你,唔比同外國人傾政治野咪已經限制左自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"836672856682f707903a361ee3dd1b7ea269cf31","tid":2087110,"uid":123774,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T14:52:58.000Z","msg":"支那狗喺度說三道四"},{"pid":"1df9738e0243f6069401673248c95e7e1181fb8f","tid":2087110,"uid":25424,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T14:55:15.000Z","msg":"取消貿易最惠待遇啦，仲講乜鳩同內地不同獨特城市呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60320bea35cebb54508237